      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owners. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor road rash on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger door. Mechanically, the car is solid with a smooth-shifting transmission and a clean engine bay, though the tires will likely need replacement within the next 10,000 miles. Inside, the upholstery is clean and free of tears, making this a reliable and presentable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
