    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely pristine vehicle that looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! This car is in truly mint condition, meticulously maintained and cared for with no signs of wear inside or out. It\u2019s a rare find for a discerning buyer who appreciates a vehicle in flawless, showroom-quality shape. Experience the smooth, powerful performance of a car that has been kept in peak condition!",
