    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am absolutely heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom! It's been pampered, garage-kept, and is basically flawless inside and out. If you\u2019ve been looking for a total gem that\u2019s been loved with all my heart, you just found it! Come see it for yourself and fall in love!",
      "price": 43900.0,
