    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that delivers a razor-sharp throttle response and a linear power band to its 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-variable differential lock. Mechanically, this specimen is beyond reproach: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings and VANOS hub have been addressed with documented precision. The chassis retains its factory-fresh rigidity, riding on a perfectly damped suspension with zero bushing deflection. Finished in concours-level condition with impeccable paint depth and a pristine interior, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Garage kept. Flawless original paint. Interior is factory clean. Full service history included. No accidents. Mechanically perfect.",
      "price": 43500.0,
