      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-grade vehicle that has been preserved with obsessive attention to detail. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional multi-stage ceramic coating, the exterior is entirely free of rock chips, swirls, or door dings. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the original alloy wheels are pristine, currently wrapped in a fresh set of premium performance tires with less than 500 miles of wear. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the leather seats show zero bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since day one, and the dashboard is free of any UV fading or cracking. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and features a comprehensive, documented service history with all scheduled maintenance performed by certified technicians. From the spotless engine bay to the bone-dry undercarriage, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. Included in the sale are both original keys, the window sticker, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a detailed binder of service receipts. This is an investment-grade example suited for the most discerning collector.",
